+
+Reviewed commits since the prior architecture review (`0939e01`):
+- `002EYA-e2e-baseline-and-seed-safety` (`e8a166f`) plus operator baseline commit `9c4e97b`
+- `002F2-navigation-render-regression-tests` (`17a85e6`)
