+- [ ] Execution plan written
+- [ ] Tests written first
+- [ ] Code implemented
+- [ ] API contracts updated, if needed
+- [ ] Permissions tested
+- [ ] Audit/session side effects tested
+- [ ] Visual evidence saved, if frontend is touched
+- [ ] Tests/typecheck/lint/build passed
+- [ ] Risk assessment completed
